@baseUrl = http://localhost:8015
@apiKey = dev-demo-key

### Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Ask governance question
POST {{baseUrl}}/agent/ask
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
X-User-Id: alice@contoso.com
X-Role: viewer
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "Who can approve sensitive identity control actions?"
}

### Perform non-sensitive action (operator)
POST {{baseUrl}}/agent/action
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
X-User-Id: bob@contoso.com
X-Role: operator
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action_type": "create_task",
  "payload": {
    "title": "Investigate high-risk sign-in",
    "owner": "soc-analyst"
  }
}

### Perform sensitive action (requires approval)
POST {{baseUrl}}/agent/action
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
X-User-Id: bob@contoso.com
X-Role: operator
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action_type": "call_mock_graph_endpoint",
  "payload": {
    "endpoint": "/users/{id}/block-signin",
    "target": "user@contoso.com"
  }
}

### Approve sensitive action as admin (replace id)
POST {{baseUrl}}/agent/approvals/2
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
X-User-Id: admin@contoso.com
X-Role: admin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "decision": "approve",
  "reviewer_notes": "Validated against incident severity and policy."
}

### Retrieve action logs
GET {{baseUrl}}/agent/actions/logs?limit=50
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
X-User-Id: admin@contoso.com
X-Role: admin
